node.text:
It’s DOPE to accept a RAD IMPACT AWARD for inspiring purpose! AND I get to share this award with someone who inspires me -- Raquel Simpson-- and my charity @cactusjackfoundation.

This RAD Impact Award provides several Waymon Webster Scholarships to empower and enrich deserving students at HBCUs. This award means the world to me because we get to share the power of education!

Thank you @radvocacy and @amazonfashion #RADonLuxuryStores for supporting my vision of a world where deserving students get the boost they need to achieve their dreams. Join me in creating a #RADNewWorld for all!

@cactusjack
